Stop Forum Spam Plugin for Unclassified Newsboard

This plugin checks the provided username, email address and current IP
address of anyone who attempts to register against the API provided
by http://www.stopforumspam.com

If a match was found, the user registration will be denied. Denials are
logged in the standard UNB log.

To install copy the stopforumspam.* files into your unb_lib/plugins folder.


